inity, Sorare, or Star Atlas and we are going to do our part to see how the gaming industry will change for good very soon after the arrival of blockchain.</span>', 'WTF are NFTs?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'wtf-are-nfts', '', '', '2022-01-14 05:29:22', '2022-01-14 02:29:22', '', 0, 'https://jollity.app/blog/?p=171', 0, 'post', '', 0),
